data.description: Welcome home to this roomy 5 BR/2 BA home located only 4 miles from New Hope schools! Enjoy making cozy fires this fall in the bricked, wood-burning fireplace; a focal point in the spacious living room. The kitchen boasts all stainless steel appliances and plenty of counter space for meal prep as well as an additional eating area. The two end bedrooms were added in 2016, have large double closets and their own HVAC unit. The laundry room opens up to the garage utility room providing easy accessibility inside and out. The backyard boasts a fenced 20 x 40 in-ground pool with nearby hot tub and plenty of patio space. There's also a wired storage building & 18 x 36 2-bay wired shop. 2.5 acres of land allow you plenty of room to roam, garden, or expand your outdoor entertainment options!
